  (lib_symbols)

  (text "MCU SUBSYSTEM\n\nFunction:\n- PWM generation for gate driver\n- ADC for current sensing\n- SPI for temperature sensor\n- I2C for display/sensors\n- Safety enable output\n- Watchdog kick signal\n- Zero-crossing detection\n- WiFi/BLE communication\n\nKey Components:\n- ESP32-S3-WROOM-1-N4\n- 3.3V decoupling capacitors\n- USB-C programming connector\n- Reset/boot buttons\n- Debug header\n\nPWM Configuration:\n- Frequency: 20-100kHz\n- Dead-time: 500ns minimum\n- RC filter: 51Ω + 33pF\n\nReference: ESP32-S3 Datasheet"
